# These are sanitized detection FIXTURES, not real dotenv files. The repo-root
# .gitignore excludes `.env.*` (keeping only `.env.example`), which would silently
# drop the env-template fixtures below — re-include them here so they stay tracked.
# (Verified with `git check-ignore`; a nested negation overrides the parent pattern.)
!.env.shared.example
!*.env.*-dist
!*.dist
